Informative site
-Promote online security 
-Recommend best practices 

Easy to use Internet Map tool
-Simple and clear interface 
-Provide lookup for Instagram and Facebook data 
-Location Data is pinned to a google map
-Ablity to drill down on map pins to get the source image/post 

Share function 
-Ablity to share your map to social media 

Secure site 
-HTTPS
-Map will not provide data from the last 24 hrs as not to be used as a stalking tool 

Advertisement 
-Sections on the page for online security products (VPNS, Password managers, etc)